### Ver intrumentos
GET http://localhost:3000/instruments

### Crear instrumento
POST http://localhost:3000/instruments
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "symbol": "AAPL",
    "name": "Apple Inc.",
    "type": "stock",
    "exchange": "NASDAQ",
    "currency": "USD",
    "active": true
}

###Crear indicador
POST http://localhost:3000/indicators
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "instrumentId": "69d5a9df3bb7fd32bd3832b1",
    "symbol": "AAPL",
    "timeframe": "1h",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-08T00:00:00.000Z",
    "type": "MACD",
    "macd": {
        "macdLine": 10,
        "signalLine": 5,
        "histogram": 5,
        "ema12": 100,
        "ema26": 95
    }
}

### Ver indicadores
GET http://localhost:3000/indicators